    "label": "Figure",
    "content": "<img alt=\"Diagram showing the Supply Chain Resilience Management Framework. The center is '群創光電' (Innolux). The framework is divided into two main areas: '營運持續管理機制' (Operational Continuity Management Mechanism) and '建置營運持續e化系統' (Establishment of Operational Continuity e-System). The Operational Continuity Management Mechanism includes: 1. 供應商持續現況調查、制定營運管理目標與政策; 2. 開辦系列講座與課程; 3. 供應商營運持續計畫(BCP)演練推動、檢討改善. The Operational Continuity e-System includes: 1. 規劃系統架構與作業程序; 2. 系統作業分析報表; 3. 系統測試與導入訓練: 群創、供應商.\"/>",
